1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Caught Having an Affair
with the Crown Prince)

4
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,240
And

5
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:57,880
Wangshi Tower

6
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,470
also played a major part.

7
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,200
Wang...

8
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:04,950
Wangshi Tower?

9
00:01:05,350 --> 00:01:07,120
I told you Pan Yang was a lapdog.

10
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,840
See? He even answered the call.

11
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,760
How dare you offend Miss Qingqing.

12
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,710
Now get to the Court of Judicial Review

13
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,920
and take thirty strokes.

14
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,400
Do you understand?

15
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:23,150
Your Highness,
I... I didn't do anything wrong.

16
00:01:23,510 --> 00:01:23,840
I...

17
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,680
So what?

18
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,280
You don't have to go.

19
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,840
Then leave your life behind.

20
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,840
Understood, Your Highness.

21
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:34,760
I'll go at once.

22
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,840
Muyan,

23
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,590
Husband and wife
should stand by each other.

24
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,590
Aren't you going too?

25
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,310
Qingqing, Yang was the one who wanted...

26
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:53,560
Thirty strokes or a slash from my blade.

27
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,480
Your choice.

28
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,120
I know I was wrong.

29
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,950
But I'm with child.

30
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,350
Then you'll take the cane instead.

31
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,070
Yes.

32
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:08,400
Thank... Thank you, Your Highness.

33
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,150
Move! Go!

34
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:21,800
Miss Qingqing,

35
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,840
I found this on the street.

36
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,520
It must be Yuanhe trying
to drive a wedge between us.

37
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,260
(It's hard to meet, and harder still to part.
The east wind is weak, and the flowers wither.)

38
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:27,980
(As silkworms spin silk until death,
candles burn to ashes before their tears run dry.)

39
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,030
You're right.

40
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:33,000
It really is an attempt
to drive us apart.

41
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,590
Yuanhe,

42
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,470
what do you have to say?

43
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,840
(Those details...)

44
00:02:47,010 --> 00:02:48,990
(How could the Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower know?)

45
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,190
(She's been
watching Qingqing all along.)

46
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,230
(I can't let Qingqing be put in danger.)

47
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:58,030
Father, this must be the Tower Master's
scheme to drive us apart.

48
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,520
Then why is the entire Capital

49
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,570
filled with rumors
about you and the Tower Master?

50
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,520
They're nothing more
than baseless rumors.

51
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,310
I will get to the bottom of this.

52
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:13,030
Yuanhe,

53
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,310
you should conduct yourself
with greater restraint.

54
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,910
Even if they're only rumors,

55
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,910
they still show your poor judgment

56
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,630
and lack of discipline.

57
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,890
If this happens again,

58
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,150
I will punish you without mercy.

59
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,280
Yes.

60
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,630
You may leave now.

61
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,280
Father,

62
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,680
the Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower has gone too far.

63
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,080
She actually dared to frame Yuanhe.

64
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:54,910
Why don't you send someone

65
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:56,280
to protect Yuanhe now?

66
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:59,120
Ever since Yuanhe took over
the affairs of Wangshi Tower,

67
00:03:59,230 --> 00:04:01,310
he's often busy
at Wangshi Tower until late at night.

68
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,690
What if the Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower

69
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,710
catches Yuanhe off guard

70
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,190
and makes a move against him?

71
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:10,030
Yuanhe often visits Wangshi Tower?

72
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,240
That's right.

73
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:16,680
(It's where
the rebel Tower Master is hiding.)

74
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,160
Your Highness.

75
00:04:23,290 --> 00:04:24,870
Have someone secretly protect Qingqing.

76
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,560
She may be in danger.

77
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:27,270
Yes.

78
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,600
What about the Tower Master?

79
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:30,820
She's living on borrowed time.

80
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:32,830
She won't be around much longer.

81
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,680
Send someone
to find someone close to Qingqing.

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,090
Tell them I want to see her.

83
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,360
At Wangshi Tower.

84
00:04:46,390 --> 00:04:47,240
Tell her

85
00:04:47,870 --> 00:04:49,680
I have a deal to discuss with her.

86
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,160
Yes.

87
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:54,780
(Wangshi Tower)

88
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:02,270
(Since those little tabloids
can't stop you,)

89
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,660
(don't blame me for showing no mercy.)

90
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:05,080
(At the end of the Wei Hour,
Wangshi Tower is willing to fully arm itself)

91
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:05,500
(in exchange for helping the Crown Prince
ascend to the highest position.)

92
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,020
(I only ask that
Your Highness spare my life.)

93
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,800
Your Highness.

94
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:19,780
Did Your Highness summon me
because you have something to discuss?

95
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:21,790
Take a look at this new crossbow.

96
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,150
I've improved the original design

97
00:05:23,170 --> 00:05:24,560
by adding an interlocking mechanism.

98
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:26,340
It takes thirty percent less effort
to draw the string.

99
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,830
It can fire three bolts in succession.

100
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,240
A repeating crossbow?

101
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:36,690
(He even managed
to recreate Zhuge's repeating crossbow.)

102
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:39,070
(His talent for craftsmanship
is truly exceptional.)

103
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:42,430
If this crossbow can be mass produced,

104
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,340
it will greatly strengthen
our border defenses.

105
00:05:44,350 --> 00:05:47,300
The Ministry of War is preparing
to manufacture a new batch of crossbows.

106
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:49,630
I heard your family
owns a timber business.

107
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:52,000
(A timber order.)

108
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,390
(This is a huge deal.)

109
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:55,360
(I've already ruined
so many business opportunities.)

110
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,390
(I was just worrying about money.)

111
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,990
(I'll earn it back
with his craftsmanship.)

112
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,180
(This is definitely worth it.)

113
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,600
(He owed me this anyway.)

114
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:03,600
It would be my honor

115
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,680
to contribute to the border defenses.

116
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:09,510
We'll just need to work out
the details of our partnership.

117
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:12,240
I can teach you
how to make the repeating crossbow.

118
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,630
We'll work together.

119
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,820
You keep eighty percent
of the profits, and I'll take twenty.

120
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,190
(He's only taking twenty percent?)

121
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:20,870
(What does he really want from me?)

122
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,510
This is a matter of great importance.

123
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:26,600
If Your Highness entrusts it to me,

124
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,830
won't His Majesty object?

125
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:29,830
It's fine.

126
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,460
At most, I'll just kneel for three days.

127
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,510
That's right.

128
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,920
To protect you, His Highness

129
00:06:34,930 --> 00:06:36,990
was fiercely criticized by the Second Prince
before the imperial court.

130
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,240
He nearly had to give up
the Inspectorate's authority

131
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,870
to oversee investigations.

132
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:39,430
Chang Lin.

133
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:51,630
(Would this move her even a little?)

134
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,190
(What a pity.)

135
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:57,480
(This scheming fool from the Inspectorate
keeps ruining my businesses every day.)

136
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,880
(The sooner he's gone, the better.)

137
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:02,720
I had no idea Your Highness
was punished because of me.

138
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:04,190
I'm truly ashamed.

139
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,040
It's nothing.

140
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,720
(Why was he only made to kneel?)

141
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:13,510
(As long as
this scheming fool stays alive,)

142
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,680
(my grand plan to make money
will never go smoothly.)

143
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,070
(Kill him?)

144
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:28,630
It seems I have
the perfect opportunity right now.

145
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,040
What opportunity?

146
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,560
(I can reall
get rid of him that easily?)

147
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:46,120
(Is this scheming fool
setting a trap for me?)

148
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,390
(Forget it.)

149
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,510
How... How did you do that?

150
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,630
Every shot hit the bull's eye.

151
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:01,190
Besides improving
your aim through practice,

152
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:02,790
there's also a trick
to drawing the string.

153
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,510
Look.

154
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:06,800
Right here.

155
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:08,360
There's a small raised notch.

156
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,070
Place your finger here

157
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:18,630
and draw the string.

158
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:23,990
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

159
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,160
This way, it's not only silent

160
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,360
but also faster.

161
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,870
Every arrow finds its mark.

162
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:33,870
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

163
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:37,550
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

164
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,200
In an instant,

165
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,120
you can

166
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,440
kill with a single shot.

167
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:45,890
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

168
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:48,230
♪Though fate tries♪

169
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:50,810
♪To make us pass each other by♪

170
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,960
(If she ever runs into danger,)

171
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,790
(she should be able to protect herself.)

172
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,960
That's amazing.

173
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,890
Do you know any other techniques
that can kill with a single strike?

174
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,670
Of course.

175
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:03,000
I'll teach you slowly in the future.

176
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:04,320
Thank you, Your Highness.

177
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:06,150
I'll make sure to learn well.

178
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,390
(So I can use them all to kill you.)

179
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:10,390
(She's finally willing
to let me get close.)

180
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:14,830
♪Your smiling face♪

181
00:09:14,830 --> 00:09:17,730
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

182
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:20,510
♪Our love will never fade away♪

183
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:22,510
(Why isn't Yuanzhao here yet?)

184
00:09:22,530 --> 00:09:24,120
(The atmosphere is getting so intimate.)

185
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,910
(I'll be at a disadvantage soon.)

186
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,510
The Imperial Guards are here!

187
00:09:29,530 --> 00:09:31,290
Remaining members
of Wangshi Tower, come out!

188
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:36,510
Meeting Your Highness in private
was already improper.

189
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:38,590
Now I'm being called
an accomplice of Wangshi Tower.

190
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:38,960
What...

191
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,960
What should I do?

192
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:07,600
Yuanhe,

193
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,270
why are you here?

194
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:12,870
I've already bought this place
as my private residence.

195
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,600
Didn't you know?

196
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,320
Your Highness,

197
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,510
we received a secret report

198
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,630
saying the Tower Master
would appear here today.

199
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,480
Have you seen her?

200
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,000
Commander Wei,

201
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,030
I think

202
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:29,630
there must be
some misunderstanding here.

203
00:10:30,810 --> 00:10:32,510
Who is the woman
in Your Highness's arms?

204
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,960
Why is she hiding
and afraid to show herself?

205
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,000
Don't worry.

206
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,510
Commander Wei,
are you trying to investigate me?

207
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,030
Since I act under His Majesty's orders,

208
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,230
I must investigate this thoroughly.

209
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:47,870
How dare you!

210
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,360
The Crown Prince's affairs

211
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,000
are not something a mere Commander
of the Imperial Guards like you

212
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,720
can question.

213
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,390
Commander Wei has always been like this.

214
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:55,840
Yuanhe,

215
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,030
you know that too.

216
00:11:06,710 --> 00:11:10,070
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

217
00:11:10,830 --> 00:11:14,230
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

218
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:16,750
♪Your smile♪

219
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:19,270
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

220
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:22,950
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

221
00:11:23,430 --> 00:11:26,750
♪Yet I stand before you♪

222
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:31,310
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

223
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:33,630
♪Though fate tries♪

224
00:11:33,630 --> 00:11:36,230
♪To make us pass each other by♪

225
00:11:36,430 --> 00:11:39,870
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

226
00:11:40,110 --> 00:11:41,750
♪Though time slips by♪

227
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,510
♪As day turns into night♪

228
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:48,070
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

229
00:11:48,470 --> 00:11:50,870
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

230
00:11:50,870 --> 00:11:52,630
♪Blessed by fate♪

231
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:57,790
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

232
00:11:57,790 --> 00:12:00,230
♪Your smiling face♪

233
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:03,070
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

234
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:06,710
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

235
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:10,670
♪And wander the world together♪

236
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,030
♪Holding you close♪

237
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:14,550
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

238
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:16,870
♪Your tenderness♪

239
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:19,750
♪Is the brightest moon♪

240
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:23,430
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

241
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:27,270
♪Our love will never fade away♪

242
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:29,710
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

243
00:12:30,230 --> 00:12:34,510
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

244
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:46,150
♪Your smiling face♪

245
00:12:46,310 --> 00:12:48,910
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

246
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:53,070
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

247
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:56,790
♪And wander the world together♪

248
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,110
♪Holding you close♪

249
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,750
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

250
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:03,030
♪Your tenderness♪

251
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:05,870
♪Is the brightest moon♪

252
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:09,630
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

253
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:13,430
♪Our love will never fade away♪

254
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:16,070
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

255
00:13:16,350 --> 00:13:20,470
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪
